transcript:
Customer: Hello.

Customer: Hello.
Executive: Namaste, main baat kar raha hu IndiaMART se.
Customer: Haan, Naman bhai.
Executive: Ji, main keh raha tha ki woh aapne kal IndiaMART mein complain kiya tha ki aapko kuch leads nahi aa rahi hai issue.
Customer: Haan yaar, bhaiya lead ka bahut jyada issue aa raha hai abhi. Har baar aapka naam bolte ki.
Executive: Aapke system mein?
Customer: Abhi main bahar aa rakha hu, yaha thoda customer milne.
Executive: Kitni der mein pahuchenge aap?
Customer: Lagengay ek do ghante toh.
Executive: Theek hai, aap pahunch ke ek baar phone kariye hume.
Customer: Theek hai sir.
